title: VonZipper : Wil Hahn in The Beefy Motocross Goggle
description:
Wil Hahn has been appointed as the Ride Captain of our FreeWheelers MX club!! Welcome to the team!

A bone in cut from the VZ meat locker. The VonZipper Beefy motorcycle goggle will convert even the most die-hard vegetarian into a carnivore. The forward venting in the frame and wide field of vision create a savory fillet of goggle au jous that is slow cooked to perfection.
